1) What two pieces of information does the client need in order to make a connection with a
server?
Ans. IP address and Port number

2) Which TCP port numbers are reserved for “well-known services” like HTTP and FTP?
Ans. HTTP - 80, FTP - 20 and 21

3) TRUE or FALSE: The range of valid TCP port numbers can be represented
   by a short primitive.
Ans. False